{{单双书号转换|'''痛苦之屋'''}}（{{lang-en|"House of Pain"}}）是美國搖滾樂團[[Faster_Pussycat|Faster Pussycat]]錄製的[[抒情歌曲#强力谣曲|强力谣曲]]<ref>{{cite web|publisher=[[AllMusic|AllMusic]]|last=Huey|first=Steve|url=http://www.allmusic.com/album/wake-me-when-its-over-mw0000204450|title=Wake Me WhenIt's Over - Faster Pussycat|accessdate=2017-05-30|archive-date=2017-06-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170618012747/http://www.allmusic.com/album/wake-me-when-its-over-mw0000204450|dead-url=no}}</ref>，收錄於專輯《[[結束時叫醒我|結束時叫醒我]]》（''Wake Me When It's Over''）中。歌曲廣受歡迎，在[[告示牌百强单曲榜|《告示牌》百强单曲榜]]上登上第28位。<ref name="Billboard Hot 100">{{cite web|publisher=[[Prometheus_Global_Media|Prometheus Global Media]]|work=[[告示牌_(雜誌)|Billboard]]|url=http://www.billboard.com/artist/302017/faster-pussycat/chart|title=Faster Pussycat - Chart history|accessdate=2017-05-30|archive-date=2017-02-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170207045439/http://www.billboard.com/artist/302017/faster-pussycat/chart|dead-url=no}}</ref>

該歌曲的[[音樂錄影帶|MV]]由[[麥可·貝|麥可·貝]]執導。<ref>{{cite web|publisher=IMVDb|url=https://imvdb.com/video/faster-pussycat/house-of-pain|title=Faster Pussycat-House of Pain (1989)|accessdate=2017-07-01|archive-date=2020-11-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201114092222/https://imvdb.com/video/faster-pussycat/house-of-pain|dead-url=no}}</ref>

